.sp
TIME specify the countdown time in format of NUMBER[SUFFIX], SUFFIX can be \(aqd\(aq, \(aqh\(aq, \(aqm\(aq, \(aqs\(aq. Default is \(aqs\(aq if SUFFIX is omitted. TIME can be used multiple times and they will be summed up.
